data.name: Ramble Vanble! 2020 ford transit
data.filtered_description:
2020 Ford Transit 250

Fuel your adventure with the "Ramble Vanble". Ramble Vanble is a 148" camper van that is cozy, quaint, and has everything you need. Let this 2020 Transit cruise you to your next adventure. It boasts high ceilings making it comfortable to walk around in, but it fits in a standard parking spot. This camper van is perfect for those wanting to experience the van life while still having an easy drive and everyday amenities.  

Pets Welcome :) Magnetic dog waste bag dumpster included on the back of the van.  

Power: 400W solar system with 400 amp hour 12V battery system.  3000W inverter. Plenty of power to charge phones, power the cooktop, fans, and refrigerator.  Additionally, wifi hotspot allows you to connect wherever you travel. 

AC/Cooling: Our van is fully insulated, and the MaxxAir fan, dehumidifier, and plug-in fans make this a comfortable temperature even in the summer! Open up the doors and let the breeze through while keeping the bugs out with bug nets on the sliding door, front windows, and side window. A/C only while the van is running

Sleeping: our van is perfect for a traveling duo or a solo traveler.  There are two seats up front, and the passenger seat swivels.  The couch folds out into a bed with memory foam cushions, a mattress cover, and all the fresh linens, pillows, and comfy blankets you will need.  

Kitchen: butcher block countertops, removable kitchen table, and refrigerator make this little van kitchen top-notch. There is plenty of storage for food, and the cabinets are stocked with all your favorite kitchen gadgets, including an induction cooktop, blender, and single-serving coffee maker.  

Bathroom: enjoy a full indoor shower with a water heater as well as a NaturesHead composting toilet.  

Check us out in Instagram: @theramblevanble
data.description_included:
Fresh linens, wifi hotspot, travel pillows, cookware - induction cooktop, pot, 8" wok, 10" carbon steel pan, 8" nonstick pan, plates, bowls, cups, coffee mugs, utensils, knives, dish soap, hand soap, cutting board, coffee maker with K-cup or ground coffee option, magic bullet mini blender, and herbs/spices.

Available upon request, Propane camping stove, beach chairs, beach games, pickup from Wilmington airport, or delivery within a 20-mile radius.

data.name: 2024 Forest River R-Pod 202
data.filtered_description:
The R-pod 202 camper is your ticket to a world of adventure, relaxation, and memories to last a lifetime. You'll love how easy it is to tow and set up, how comfortable and stylish the interior is, and the freedom it grants to explore both on and off the grid. Whether you're planning a scenic road trip, a peaceful retreat in nature, or a festival-hopping excursion, this camper is your trusty companion. Enjoy the great outdoors without sacrificing comfort, and embrace the nomadic spirit in style.

The R-pod 202 camper is loaded with essential amenities to elevate your camping adventure. Thanks to its solar capabilities and sturdy Curt suspension, towing is a breeze whether you're navigating rough terrains or cruising down the highway. What's more, it's incredibly campground-friendly, requiring only a 30 amp, 120-volt power supply, which is perfect for smaller campgrounds. Plus, the built-in outdoor griddle and refrigerator bring added convenience to your outdoor experience. And with a handy bike rack, you can easily bring your bicycles along for even more exploration. These features combine to make your camping journey both effortless and exhilarating.
data.description_included: Your R-pod 202 camper rental comes with a selection of inclusions for your comfort and convenience. Inside, you'll find linens provided, saving you the hassle of packing bedding. Step outside, and you'll discover 2x folding rocking chairs and a portable camping table, perfect for enjoying the great outdoors. With these additional amenities, you'll be well-equipped for a memorable camping experience.

data.name: 2021 California Custom Vans - Luxury Build With Shower, Dinette, and More!
data.filtered_name: 2021 California Custom Vans - Luxury Build With Shower, Dinette, and More!
data.filtered_description:
Tanner is an open concept, modern camper built for indoor congregation and outdoor exploration alike. Throughout the build you will find a host of natural woods showcasing phenomenal grain structure from responsibly sourced lumber. Set off by luxurious black stained cabinetry, with just a hint of transparency to let you know it's the good stuff, Tanner is pure eye candy. Combine that with luxury hardware and a truly decadent backsplash and a high-end sound system, this little home on wheels is much more than just a place to rest your head.  Featuring a dinette style bed that easily morphs between sleeping for two and dining for 6, this build also accommodates sleeping for a third camper with a hidden slide-out, making Tanner perfect for small families and guests. Featuring my proprietary Hideaway Indoor Shower and an outdoor shower (both with hot water), a spacious front access fridge / freezer, overhead storage galore and a utilitarian roof system with a stylish steel fairing, this luxury home on wheels feels spacious and grande while giving you the modern amenities needed for an adventurous life on the road.

This van is powered by dual lithium batteries that receive charge from two solar panels, the van's alternator and shore power should you need it. Tanner also features an extra large awning that is easily deployable by one person. Water heats up quickly for showers both in and out of the van. Easily connect your phone to the van's head unit or the independent, high-end sound system in the rear perfect for a little dinner music or swinging the doors wide open and accompanying your fire pit with tunes.   

See the full specs and details on our website!

Tanner is also FOR Sale! Message for details.

data.name: Rent And "Runway"! - Open space 2017 Mercedes-Benz Sprinter
data.filtered_name: Rent And "Runway"! - Open space 2017 Mercedes-Benz Sprinter
data.filtered_description:
Simplicity is the thing in this "Runaway"! 
This van we named "Runaway" is a 13 feet in length (6' ceiling) cozy freedom nest that will take you places you can only imagine! Park anywhere your heart wishes to soak in the scenery. 
The open floor plan makes the van incredibly comfortable when traveling as you can convert from a full bed at night to a wide open van during the day. Conversion of Runaway was completed in 2020.

Bring your furry copilot with you!

Two seat belts only allow two people riding. Sleeps two people. 

The Van features a 12V power system with 220 AH of AGM storage. You can easily charge your phones, computers, plug in fans etc. 

Heating / Cooling: When not running on the Van's Core AC, the van relies on a 7500K Maxxair Fan which pulls air in and pushes out (Remote Control Included). The van is insulated with 300 SqFt of Havelock Wool. Extra fan included.  

Kitchenette: Butcher block counter top with tile backsplash and storage space in-between counter and cooler for camping stove. One burner butane stove included. 

Plumbing / Water Supply: The sink in the kitchenette includes a 7 gallon fresh water tank and 4 gallon grey water tank, and a hand pump faucet.

Bathroom: No typical bathroom. We use designed toilet seat with biodegradable bags and that perfectly works for us. We use portable shower designed as a bag with a shower head attachment to be used outside. 

Sleeping: Two leaves store under the driver side bench and unfold in-between both benches creating a full size bed. The cushions are a full size 6" memory foam mattress, super comfortable!

Living Space: Front passenger seat swivels and can be used for additional living space seating. Driver bench features a 12"x36" wood pull out on 500 lbs. rated slides that can be used as an outside table or cook top.

Outdoor Living Space: Rooftop patio!  Our favorite.  Features 5'x6' patio made of treated lumber.

data.name: 2022 Coachmen Chaparral 2 full baths!
data.filtered_description:
Welcome to the world of premium RV rentals with our stunning 2022 Coachmen Chaparral 373Mbrb. Whether you're planning a family vacation, a couples' getaway, or a road trip with friends, this meticulously designed fifth wheel offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Get ready to embark on an unforgettable adventure with all the conveniences of home on the road.

**Exterior Features:**

- **Quality Craftsmanship:** The Coachmen Chaparral is known for its exceptional build quality, ensuring a safe and reliable journey for you and your loved ones.

- **Smooth Towing:** Featuring an aerodynamic front cap, this fifth wheel cuts through the wind for a seamless towing experience. Set up is a breeze with the electric front and rear stabilizer jacks.

- **Outdoor Entertainment:** Take your relaxation outdoors with the exterior entertainment center, complete with a large LED TV and speakers. Perfect for enjoying a movie night under the stars or catching the game while tailgating.

- **Storage Galore:** With spacious pass-through storage compartments and a rear garage, you'll have plenty of room for all your gear, bikes, and outdoor equipment.

**Interior Features:**

- **Spacious Living Area:** The living area is designed for relaxation, featuring comfortable seating, a cozy fireplace, and a large LED TV. It's the ideal spot to unwind after a day of adventure.

- **Gourmet Kitchen:** The fully equipped kitchen boasts solid surface countertops, a residential refrigerator, a three-burner cooktop, and a generous pantry. Cooking on the road has never been this enjoyable.

- **Private Master Suite:** The luxurious master bedroom includes a king-size bed, a wardrobe with washer/dryer prep, and an en-suite bathroom with a spacious shower and solid surface countertops.

- **Bunkhouse:** A separate bunkhouse provides a private space for kids or guests, complete with its own bathroom and entertainment center.

- **Comfortable Sleeping Arrangements:** In addition to the master bedroom and bunkhouse, the living area sofa converts into a bed, and the dinette offers additional sleeping space, accommodating up to 9 people.

**Additional Features:**

- **Four Slides:** This fifth wheel features four slide-outs, offering extra space and a roomy interior.

- **Climate Control:** Stay comfortable year-round with the dual-zone air conditioning and heating system.

- **High-End Finishes:** The Chaparral 373Mbrb is adorned with premium cabinetry, residential-style fixtures, and elegant lighting throughout.

- **Smart Technology:** Stay connected with the built-in Bluetooth audio system, USB charging ports, and optional Wi-Fi capabilities.

Experience the epitome of luxury and convenience with our 2022 Coachmen Chaparral 373Mbrb rental. It's your passport to unforgettable adventures and cherished memories on the road. Contact Mtrv Rentals today to reserve your dream getaway on wheels!

data.name: Cozy Camper Camping Company
data.filtered_description:
Welcome to the Cozy Camper Camping Company! Your next adventure awaits! Now renting our brand new 2022 Heartland Pioneer QB300. This cozy farmhouse camper sleeps up to 8 guests. With a private queen room in the front, a private bunk house in the back and a large 14 foot slide. out. You’ll have all the room you need! The bunk house can sleep up to four with a bottom bunk/dinette conversion. This camper can sleep up to 8 and has one full bath. The features are not just on the inside but also outside. We all love the beach but hate the sand. That’s why we equipped our camper with an outdoor shower that has hot and cold water! With an outdoor awning over LED lights, you’ll be sitting around the fire in style! Love music but hate carrying around a Bluetooth speaker? We got you covered with speakers on the inside and outside! 

New to RVing? No experience towing? Or just do not want to deal with the hassle of setting up? This is the camper for you! We strictly deliver to homes and campsites. What’s included with our delivery fee?  Setup and tear down! We will cover the features of the camper and answer any questions you may have. All you have to do is show up with yourselves, food, drinks and a great attitude! 
 ***This Camper is Delivery Only***

***Once Camper is Parked it Will Not Be Moved***
data.description_included:
We give you all the necessities needed to make your trip a breeze! All beds come made with fresh linens and pillows. The bathroom will come stocked with fresh towels. 

The kitchen comes with bowls, plates, cups and utensils for 8! Do not forget about the 2 pots and 2 oven pans that are included with this rental. Nothing worse than carrying around a coffee maker…. So we included a Keurig as well.  For an additional fee you can upgrade to a Nespresso. 

2 TVs come standard! Both are smart TVs with a 24 inch in the bunkhouse and 50inch… yup 50 inch in the living area! So you can still watch game day and feel great about it!

data.filtered_description: Hi everyone! We recently purchased this awesome 27' (33' exterior) 2024 Forest River Wildwood X-Lite travel trailer, and we are looking to share with as many people as possible to make your travel experience much more relaxing, convenient, and enjoyable. Starting from the front it comes with a king-sized bed in the primary bedroom with a 43" Smart TV for your leisure. In the living space you will find a 50" Smart TV above the fireplace next to the convertible living and dining seats. In the kitchen we have an oven, stove top, microwave, refrigerator and freezer (and a Keurig for the coffee lovers). We have an indoor and outdoor shower at your disposal. In the back of the trailer is a separate room that has 3 bunk beds and a pull-out couch for extra sleeping spaces. On the outside we have a 16' retractable awning and exterior speakers for entertainment. The trailer also has a grill and mini fridge stowed away on the outside of the trailer for outdoor cooking and use. Last but not least, the trailer will have hotspot Wifi so you do not have to miss out on the important things while you are out. I can go on and on, but we will just let you see for yourselves! If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to reach out! Happy Camping!
